[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":304},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F":281,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F":290},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F12\u002Flearn-hexo-29-imgur-quick-upload\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":264,"date":265,"description":18,"extension":266,"lang":267,"meta":268,"navigation":269,"path":270,"readingMinutes":271,"seo":272,"standalone":273,"stem":274,"tags":275,"tldr":278,"updated":278,"url":279,"__hash__":280},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F29-試著學-Hexo-奇淫技巧-快速上傳你的圖片到-imgur.md","(29) 試著學 Hexo - 奇淫技巧 - 快速上傳你的圖片到 imgur","473855281",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":257},"minimark",[11,15,19,29,32,41,44,47,50,57,61,75,78,88,94,106,112,115,117,125,133,136,142,145,200,203,206,212,215,218,221,244,247,250,253],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來來講講如何透過 VSCode 快速上傳圖片到 imgur 吧！",[20,21,22],"blockquote",{},[16,23,24,28],{},[25,26,27],"strong",{},"Note","\n本系列是針對 Imgur 來做介紹，但是 Imgur 在 2025 年 05 月 16 日之後限制台灣 IP 使用者無法上傳圖片，因此如果你是台灣使用者的話，可能會無法使用 Imgur 上傳圖片，這邊建議可以改用其他圖片上傳服務。",[12,30,31],{"id":31},"imgur",[16,33,34,35,40],{},"前面章節「",[36,37,39],"a",{"href":38},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200922\u002F1947671490","(9) 試著學 Hexo - 圖片空間的挑選","」有講到 imgur 很好用，但有一些問題，也就是關於「他們不允許你使用「熱連結」的方式外連，也就是直接複製圖片連結」這件事。",[16,42,43],{},"但是老實講...我有莫約兩千多張圖片都是放在 imgur，所以...哎，不是。",[16,45,46],{},"如果你不在乎圖片的死活，其實 imgur 真的是一個很好用的免費老牌圖空東西，而我本身在撰寫部落格時也會混著用，這個章節原本也打算與前一篇混在一起，但是因為太長了...所以只好將這個章節獨立出一篇來講，因為接下來將會搭配一個很好用的 VSCode 套件來直接透過上傳到 imgur 並自動生成圖片連結（超方便）",[16,48,49],{},"你可以下方官方圖片看到有多方便",[16,51,52],{},[53,54],"img",{"alt":55,"src":56},"vscode-imgur","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FjPm7V6t.gif",[12,58,60],{"id":59},"imgur-api","Imgur API",[16,62,63,64,70,71],{},"首先先開啟 ",[36,65,69],{"href":66,"rel":67},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002F",[68],"nofollow","Imgur"," 並註冊登入帳號，然後點這個網址來申請 ",[36,72,60],{"href":73,"rel":74},"https:\u002F\u002Fapi.imgur.com\u002Foauth2\u002Faddclient",[68],[16,76,77],{},"然後填寫圖片紅框欄位。",[79,80,81,85],"ul",{},[82,83,84],"li",{},"Application name：隨便想，最好自己可以認得",[82,86,87],{},"Authorization type：OAuth 2 authorization without a callback URL",[16,89,90],{},[53,91],{"alt":92,"src":93},"Register an Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FbaiboMe.png",[16,95,96,97,101,102,105],{},"送出之後就會得到 ",[98,99,100],"code",{},"Client ID"," 與 ",[98,103,104],{},"Client secret","，這兩個東西請務必複製留下來。",[16,107,108],{},[53,109],{"alt":110,"src":111},"Client","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJDbWQvj.png",[16,113,114],{},"如果你不小心遺失的話，你就只好摸摸鼻子重新申請了，如果你是單純忘記 Client ID，則可以透過 Setting -> Applications 查看",[12,116,55],{"id":55},[16,118,119,120,124],{},"接下來就是替 VSCode 安裝套件，透過 VSCode 上傳圖片到 imgur，所以要去擴充套件中搜尋「",[36,121,55],{"href":122,"rel":123},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=MaxfieldWalker.vscode-imgur",[68],"」，然後安裝插件。",[16,126,127,128,101,130,132],{},"安裝完畢之後我們要設定一下剛剛再 imgur 申請的 ",[98,129,100],{},[98,131,104],{},"，否則會無法透過 VSCode 上傳到 imgur。",[16,134,135],{},"而設定的方式是打開 VSCode 的 settings.json，在新版 VSCode 進入方法是左下角齒輪>然後右上角第二個圖片",[16,137,138],{},[53,139],{"alt":140,"src":141},"settings.json","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-19%2022.16.57.png",[16,143,144],{},"接下來將下方程式碼填入即可",[146,147,152],"pre",{"className":148,"code":149,"language":150,"meta":151,"style":151},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\"vscode-imgur.client_id\": \"imgur 的 client_id\",\n\"vscode-imgur.client_secret\": \"imgur 的 client_secret\",\n\"vscode-imgur.preferUserUpload\": true,\n","json","",[98,153,154,173,186],{"__ignoreMap":151},[155,156,159,163,167,170],"span",{"class":157,"line":158},"line",1,[155,160,162],{"class":161},"sTRMh","\"vscode-imgur.client_id\"",[155,164,166],{"class":165},"sMAXC",": ",[155,168,169],{"class":161},"\"imgur 的 client_id\"",[155,171,172],{"class":165},",\n",[155,174,176,179,181,184],{"class":157,"line":175},2,[155,177,178],{"class":161},"\"vscode-imgur.client_secret\"",[155,180,166],{"class":165},[155,182,183],{"class":161},"\"imgur 的 client_secret\"",[155,185,172],{"class":165},[155,187,189,192,194,198],{"class":157,"line":188},3,[155,190,191],{"class":161},"\"vscode-imgur.preferUserUpload\"",[155,193,166],{"class":165},[155,195,197],{"class":196},"sCcAr","true",[155,199,172],{"class":165},[16,201,202],{},"這樣子就完成囉~",[16,204,205],{},"但是其實這邊有一個最後一個設置要跑，也就是關於初次上傳的部分，你先去找一個圖片隨便找，然後按下右鍵複製圖片（你沒看錯），然後回到 VSCode 中按下組合按鍵 Ctrl + Alt + v，這時候你應該會看到這個視窗",[16,207,208],{},[53,209],{"alt":210,"src":211},"PIN Code here","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-19%2022.22.58.png",[16,213,214],{},"接下來你就先停在這個視窗，因為你要回到剛剛我們沒關閉的 Imgur 畫面，這時候應該會跳出提示說，有人要透過 vscode-imgur，你只需要按下允許按鈕，然後畫面就會出現一組 PIN Code，這一段就是要貼回 VSCode 中的，那當你貼回去之後，你圖片以後就可以直接上傳到 Imgur 囉~",[12,216,217],{"id":217},"其他類似的套件",[16,219,220],{},"最後的最後，你可能會發生還有其他類似的套件",[79,222,223,230,237],{},[82,224,225],{},[36,226,229],{"href":227,"rel":228},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=Spades.vs-picgo",[68],"PicGo",[82,231,232],{},[36,233,236],{"href":234,"rel":235},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=hancel.markdown-image",[68],"Markdown Image",[82,238,239],{},[36,240,243],{"href":241,"rel":242},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=sksun27.imgur-uploader",[68],"Imgur-uploader",[16,245,246],{},"因為我個人只有使用過 vscode-imgur，所以才沒介紹其他套件，但是我稍微看了一下 Markdown Image 也相當不錯，所以你如果不喜歡我使用的這個套件，你也可以考慮上面其他三種唷~",[16,248,249],{},"而 Imgur 的設置流程應該大同小異哩~",[16,251,252],{},"那麼鐵人賽文章就到這邊結束了，不知不覺剩下兩篇了...",[254,255,256],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":151,"searchDepth":175,"depth":175,"links":258},[259,260,261,262,263],{"id":14,"depth":175,"text":14},{"id":31,"depth":175,"text":31},{"id":59,"depth":175,"text":60},{"id":55,"depth":175,"text":55},{"id":217,"depth":175,"text":217},"Hexo","2020-10-12 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F29-hexo-imgur","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F29-試著學-Hexo-奇淫技巧-快速上傳你的圖片到-imgur",[264,276,277,69],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201012\u002F473855281\u002F","0d7r7XlSDK7UOIzuS7Ko9zggCQRcPTiH7Ae3wfKgrMA",{"newer":282,"older":286},{"url":283,"title":284,"date":285},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201012\u002F1084963489\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (36) - FPS","2020-10-12 00:02:10",{"url":287,"title":288,"date":289},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201011\u002F1851462675\u002F","(28) 試著學 Hexo - 奇淫技巧 - 寫作的小眉角","2020-10-11 00:00:01",[291,295,300],{"url":292,"title":293,"date":294,"readingMinutes":271},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35",{"url":296,"title":297,"date":298,"readingMinutes":299},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","2020-11-01 13:21:00","3",{"url":301,"title":302,"date":303,"readingMinutes":271},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F","(32)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",1